name: HEN PRINCESS - Hug to Hen Project No.1 Edition
description: HEN Princess, she was born from the love of everyone here. This picture is my 1st Edition for my "Hug to HEN" project. Let's encourage our Hicetnunc artists. This is how I would like our H=N family grow up with love and friendship from around the world. We, artists, not walking alone. We have each other. Thank you for Hen's creator and everyone who always support Hicetnunc.
